panels.content:
# Memory Analytics

Memstats --> Go Tool to analyze memory usuage

GC --> Garbage Collector

Can be analyzed with pprof tool:

- `go tool pprof $GOPATH/bin/factomd http://localhost:6060/debug/pprof/profile`
- `go tool pprof $GOPATH/bin/factomd http://localhost:6060/debug/pprof/heap`
	- Inuse `go tool pprof $GOPATH/bin/factomd --inuse_space http://localhost:6060/debug/pprof/heap`
		- See top 5: `top5`
		- See line breakdown: `list FUCTION_NAME`
